===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aʊə(r)|-aʊə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# A structure, usually taller than it is wide, often used as a lookout.
#:''From the top of the '''tower''' we could see far off into the distance.''
# {{figurative}} Any item, such as a computer case, that is usually higher than it is wide.

